Method Detail

hasService

public static boolean hasService(int btClass,
                                 int serviceClass)
Returns true if the given class supports the given Service Class. A bluetooth device can claim to support zero or more service classes.

Parameters:
btClass - The bluetooth class.
serviceClass - The service class constant to test for. For example, Service.AUDIO. Must be one of the Service.FOO constants.
Returns:
True if the service class is supported.
